      "text": "Ahab's selling his film/video equipment on Facebook Marketplace. He wants help with pricing, listings, photos, and logistics. I have the gear list now. Let me organize this smartly:\n\nLighting equipment:\n- Amaran 200x (2x) - Solid LED panels, very useful\n- Amaran 100x (1x) - Same\n- Neewer LED RGB panel light (1x) - Entry-level RGB\n- 12x47in Strip Softbox (1x)\n- Octagonal Softbox (1x)\n- Lantern Softbox 20\" (1x)\n\nSupport:\n- C-Stand (1x)\n- Heavy Duty Extension Boom Arm Bar (1x)\n- Sandbags (6x)\n\nAudio:\n- Audio-Technica AT875R - solid shotgun mic, not cheap\n- Zoom H4n - solid portable recorder\n- 15ft XLR\n- Boom Pole\n\nThis is a decent kit - the Amaran lights are quality, the AT875R is a good mic, and all the support gear is useful.\n\nI should give him:\n1. Pricing guidance (general ranges for used gear)\n2. Individual listing templates he can adapt\n3. Photo tips\n4. Logistics/logistics guidance\n5. Maybe bundle suggestions\n\nLet me keep it focused and actionable.Solid kit. Here's the breakdown:\n\n## **PRICING STRATEGY**\n\n**Lighting** (usually holds value well):\n- Amaran 200x: $200-250 each (retail ~$500)\n- Amaran 100x: $120-150 (retail ~$300)\n- Neewer RGB panel: $40-60 (retail ~$120)\n- Softboxes: $20-40 each depending on condition\n- C-Stand: $30-50\n- Boom arm: $25-40\n- Sandbags (lot): $30-50\n\n**Audio** (this is your strongest gear):\n- AT875R: $80-120 (retail ~$250, solid shotgun mic)\n- Zoom H4n: $60-90 (retail ~$200, bulletproof recorder)\n- Boom pole: $15-25\n- XLR cable: $5-10\n\n**Total realistic range**: $700-1,100 depending on condition/negotiation\n\n---\n\n## **LISTING STRATEGY**\n\nCreate **2-3 category bundles** for FB Marketplace (easier to sell, less individual hassle):\n\n1. **\"Complete Lighting Kit\"** - Both Amarans + RGB panel + all softboxes + C-stand + boom arm + sandbags ($500-650)\n2. **\"Pro Audio Setup\"** - AT875R + H4n + boom pole + XLR ($180-240)\n3. **Individual listings** for people cherry-picking\n\n---\n\n**Need from you**: Photos of the gear (condition matters for pricing), and I'll write the actual listings. Want me to create templates you can customize, or actual FB-ready copy?",
